Type: Package
Package: rolltalk
Title: Rolling and Expanding Statistics Presentation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jason", "Foster", , "jason.j.foster@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Presentation of rolling and expanding statistics for
    time-series data. The 'rolltalk' package demonstrates the rolling and
    expanding statistics of the 'roll' package in a 'Quarto' presentation
    that is rendered to a PDF file with the roll_talk() function.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: https://github.com/jasonjfoster/rolltalk
BugReports: https://github.com/jasonjfoster/rolltalk/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    grDevices,
    quarto
Suggests: 
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    zoo
Config/roxygen2/old_usage: TRUE
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
SystemRequirements: Quarto CLI (https://quarto.org), LaTeX (TinyTeX
    recommended via 'quarto install tinytex')
